    • Field Detail

      • kCuramFormsAPIEnabled

        static final java.lang.String kCuramFormsAPIEnabled
        Indicates whether the CuramFormsAPI is enabled. If the value is set to false, the CuramFormsAPI will not register components and does not set fields when requested nor notify of change. Property name : curam.sessionmanagement.tabsession.curamformsapi.enabled
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values

      • kAutorecoveryEnabled

        static final java.lang.String kAutorecoveryEnabled
        Indicates whether the system automatically recovers unsaved data for users and returns them to where they were in the application if a system interruption such as a timeout occurs. This property applies to all application areas where autorecovery is supported. If the value is set to true, the system returns the user to where they were and recovers any data that users entered without saving before the interruption occurred. If the value is set to false, the system does not recover unsaved data in any areas of the application. Property name : curam.sessionmanagement.tabsession.autorecovery.enabled
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values

      • kAutorecoveryThrottleInterval

        static final java.lang.String kAutorecoveryThrottleInterval
        The delay, in milliseconds, to be applied between autorecovery post requests to the server. This property applies to all application areas where autorecovery is supported. Th default value is 500. A value less than 1 will turn autorecovery off. Property name : curam.sessionmanagement.tabsession.autorecovery.throttleinterval
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values
